        <updateDate>2020-11-17T19:48:13Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Unplug the Internet Kill Switch Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill repeals provisions that allow the President to shut down or take over the use or control of specified telecommunications services through the exercise of certain emergency powers. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
